{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "15", "m": "11", "Y": "2025"}, "time": {"H": "10", "M": "09", "S": "28"}}, "news": [{"title": "LuLu Group revives mall project in Visakhapatnam", "para": "LuLu Group International will revive its Visakhapatnam shopping mall project after a hiatus, citing circumstances beyond their control during the previous government's tenure. Chief Minister N Chandrababu Naidu's invitation prompted the revival, with construction set to begin this week and completion expected within three years, creating thousands of jobs.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/retail/lulu-group-announces-revival-of-visakhapatnam-mall-project-under-new-government/125341320?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-43836/125341320.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "retail"}, {"title": "New online system to simplify building plan approvals in Uttar Pradesh", "para": "Uttar Pradesh government is set to launch FASTPAS, a new online system for building plan approvals. This advanced platform will simplify the process and is expected to reduce fees. Trials have been successful, and the rollout is anticipated within a month. FASTPAS will replace the current OBPAS system.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/uttar-pradesh-launches-fastpas-new-online-system-for-quick-building-plan-approvals/125341290?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-66114/125341290.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "technology"}, {"title": "Maharashtra: Linking of property registration with I-T portals will curb under-reporting", "para": "The Inspector General of Registrar (IGR) has proposed linking its iSarita portal with the income tax department's systems to monitor high-value property deals. This comes after tax authorities discovered over Rs15,000 crore in unreported transactions in Vidarbha alone. The move aims to ensure capital gains tax compliance by providing direct data access to tax officials.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/technology/maharashtra-proposes-linking-property-registration-and-income-tax-portals-to-tackle-under-reporting/125341235?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-84919/125341235.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "technology"}]}